# REPRO-03: bench results committed as parquet + metadata JSON.
# The blanket *.parquet blocklist contradicted REPRO-03 — removed in
# favor of explicit whitelist patterns under bench/results/ below
# (the only path where parquet may legitimately live).
.worktrees/
secrets/
*.key
tests/_fixtures/*.json
bench/results/*
!bench/results/.gitkeep
!bench/results/real/
!bench/results/ollama/
!bench/results/runpod_pilot/
!bench/results/runpod_full/
!bench/results/runpod_v11/
!bench/results/runpod_smoke/
!bench/results/runpod_context_repair/
!bench/results/runpod_paired_chat/
!bench/results/runpod_paired_disagg/
# REPRO-03: bench results may also be committed as parquet. The blanket
# *.parquet blocklist was removed (see above) so parquet directly under
# any of the whitelisted bench subdirs is committable.

